%% LABELS: \begin{definition}[$k$-Unification]
%% LABELS: \cref{fig:bounded-contexts} defines the grammar of \emph{$k$-bounded contexts} $C^k$
%% LABELS: which denote the set of expression-contexts where the hole occurs under at most
